body:
I refuse to believe Sansa Stark has any chance of dying. Face it…at its very core this is a story about the Starks. Bran is the three eyed raven now, Arya has no business and no desire to be the Lady/Warden of the North.

Jon, bless him, has a great possibility of death.

THERE MUST ALWAYS BE A STARK IN WINTERFELL. SANSA IS THAT STARK.
